                                    Should you need an ADA accommodation to participate in a university event, program, or activity or need to request materials in an accessible format, please contact FIU’s Office of Civil Rights (OCR) at <a href="tel:+13053482785">305-348-2785</a> or <a href="mailto:accommodations@fiu.edu">accommodations@fiu.edu</a>. 
                                    All requests for ADA accommodation or accessible materials for this event must be submitted to OCR at least seven (7) business days prior to the event or at the earliest possible opportunity.
                                </small>
